file.name: TestSwagger2.yaml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: firstApi
  description: API Definition of firstApi
  version: 1.2.3
servers:
  - url: https://{customerId}.saas-app.com:{port}/v2/bla/{test}/hello
    variables:
      customerId:
        default: demo
        description: Customer ID assigned by the service provider
      port:
        enum:
          - '443'
          - '8443'
        default: '443'
      test:
        default: test1
paths:
  "/addUser":
    post:
      requestBody:
        description: Sample Payload
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                payload:
                  type: object
        required: false
      responses:
        default:
          description: Default response
  "/getUser/{userId}":
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: userId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        default:
          description: Default response
  "/":
    get:
      responses:
        default:
          description: Default response
